quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  95,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  95,1,injeer ki qasam aur Zaitoon ki
  95,2,aur tor seneen ki
  95,3,aur is aman walay shehar ki
  95,4,ke hum ne ensaan ko bohat achi soorat mein pedakiya hai
  95,5,phir ( rafta rafta ) is ( ki haalat ) ko ( badal kar ) pust se pust kar diya
  95,6,magar jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay unkay liye be intahaa ajar hai
  95,7,to ( ae aadam zaad ) phir to jaza ke din ko kyun jhutlata hai ?
  95,8,kiya khuda sab se bara haakim nahi hai ?
